verbose_text: Up-regulation of this signaling pathway can induce a variety of antioxidant enzymes and detoxifying enzymes, accelerate the enzymatic reaction, increase the expression of superoxide dismutase (SOD), glutathione and other antioxidant substances, scavenge free radicals and other oxides, and maintain the normal intracellular potential level, thus playing a role in cell protection XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR.
